Vanilla cupcakes

120g butter
160g castor sugar
5ml vanilla extract
2 eggs
240g cake flour
15ml baking powder
125ml milk
Pinch of salt

Beat butter & sugar til creamy. Add vanilla & eggs. Beat well. Add flour, baking powder and salt. Add milk. Mix. Bake at 180°C for 12mins https://t.co/7QtYtMkf0x
